text: Rajni KC is the pratinidhi sabha candidate from Kaski-2. After the helicopter crash of Rabindra Prasad Adhikari this seat was vacant. KC has been worked with congress since last 8 years. But she joined Sajha Party and be central committee member. She was vice chancellor at Pokhara University. ==References== Category:Nepalese politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
title: Rajni KC
